{"id":"features","title":"Angular 屬性","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <header class=\"marketing-banner\">\n  <h1 class=\"banner-headline no-toc no-anchor\" id=\"angular-features\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"36g8llbscy336118atcu283w1\">Angular 屬性</h1>\n</header>\n<article class=\"center-layout\">\n  <div class=\"feature-section\">\n    <div class=\"feature-header\">\n      <div class=\"text-headline\">Any app size</div>\n      <img src=\"generated/images/marketing/features/feature-icon.svg\" height=\"70px\" alt=\"Feature icon\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"feature-row\">\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Start quickly</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8t3w9h5h02ulnea5glrq5vano\">你可以從小應用開始，因為 Angular 的工具會隨著應用程式的發展不斷提供支援。<a href=\"/scaling\">瞭解更多</a></p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Enterprise capable</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e6f2e8tovvoxjfhta5x661x9f\">隨著團隊和應用程式的成長，Angular 會通過一個開箱即用的平台來支援你。這讓你可以建立可測試、可擴充套件的使用者介面，這些使用者介面會隨著它們的發展始終表現良好。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Predictable releases</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2rl4d8v6m56pzvydm1x3tlds1\">Angular 可預測的發布時間表和更新工具可幫你讓你的應用程式與框架和網路平台的最新進展保持同步。<a href=\"/guide/releases\">瞭解更多</a></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <hr>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"feature-section\">\n    <div class=\"feature-header\">\n      <div class=\"text-headline\">A great community</div>\n      <img src=\"generated/images/marketing/features/feature-icon.svg\" height=\"70px\" alt=\"Feature icon\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"feature-row\">\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Community resources</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2kglg5ydopc8zhdxxo6yp65f0\">Angular 社群是一個由許多本地組織組成的全球社群。<a href=\"resources?category=community\">瞭解更多</a></p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Education resources</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5ue2una0brztlnvm5tzevropj\">Angular 社群提供了書籍、研討會和正式培訓來幫助你入門。<a href=\"resources?category=education\">瞭解更多</a></p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Development resources</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cgiz9vke5xa1y95o6qxk6xhyy\">Angular 社群和團隊提供了一些資源來在開發的所有階段幫助你。<a href=\"resources?category=development\">瞭解更多</a></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <hr>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"feature-section\">\n    <div class=\"feature-header\">\n      <div class=\"text-headline\">Build productively</div>\n      <img src=\"generated/images/marketing/features/feature-icon.svg\" height=\"70px\" alt=\"Feature icon\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"feature-row\">\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Powerful command-line interface</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"299r782ot61rvc0j3w07cuq20\">Angular 指令行介面 (CLI) 支援啟動專案並助其發展到生產級別，從而保持團隊和專案之間的一致性。<a href=\"cli\">瞭解更多</a></p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Forms and routing</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2keg731mrxbjprf36byr5xyct\">Angular 的表單和路由是由 Angular 團隊開發和支援的，提供穩定性保障以及與平台其餘部分的良好整合。瞭解有關<a href=\"guide/forms-overview\">表單</a>和<a href=\"guide/routing-overview\">路由的</a>更多訊息。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Development tools</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4iumqg3d4j2j27okljo2g1opw\">Angular 的整合開發環境 (IDE) 工具提供自動完成和型別檢查。分析工具可以預覽你的應用程式的效能。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <hr>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"feature-section\">\n    <div class=\"feature-header\">\n      <div class=\"text-headline\">For everyone, everywhere</div>\n      <img src=\"generated/images/marketing/features/feature-icon.svg\" height=\"70px\" alt=\"Feature icon\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"feature-row\">\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Internationalization tools</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"aeq7kxkpjbu7gabvxdysp4lfj\">Angular 的國際化 (i18n) 和本地化 (l10n) 工具可幫助你的應用覆蓋世界各地的使用者。<a href=\"guide/i18n-overview\">瞭解更多</a></p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Accessibility tools</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1fcsqugif2fnv66unce8yla9u\">使用支援 ARIA 的元件、開發人員指南和內建的無障礙功能 (a11y) 測試基礎架構建立無障礙應用程式。<a href=\"guide/accessibility\">瞭解更多</a></p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature\">\n        <div class=\"feature-title\">Component libraries</div>\n        <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5uqme5x95hfknv9pddb3j86b5\">許多元件庫可供 Angular 應用程式使用。Material 元件庫是成千上萬的 Google 應用程式可以放心使用的函式庫。瞭解有關<a href=\"https://material.angular.io/\">Angular Material</a>的更多訊息。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <hr>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"cta-bar announcement-bar\">\n    <a class=\"button\" href=\"quick-start\">Try Angular</a>\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n  \n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - index\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /guide/releases\n - /scaling\n - cli\n - guide/accessibility\n - guide/forms-overview\n - guide/i18n-overview\n - guide/routing-overview\n - quick-start\n - resources?category=community\n - resources?category=development\n - resources?category=education\n - https://material.angular.io/\n-->"}